530
00:36:11,340 --> 00:36:14,980
If we plan it out perfectly, there's no way that guy can escape.

531
00:36:15,510 --> 00:36:18,680
We'll grab him and won't let go until he spits out the truth.

532
00:36:21,420 --> 00:36:23,390
